        <num>CC 3020</num>
        <heading>Relations Between the Principal and Third Persons</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Subsection B.  Relations Between the Principal and Third Persons
Art. 3020.  Obligations of the principal to third persons
The principal is bound to perform the contract that the mandatary, acting within the limits of his authority, makes with a third person.</p>
        </content>
